\begin_layout Standard
在碰撞前相对于圆盘-
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

 静止的惯性系中，有如下矢量关系
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta\vec{r}'=\Delta\vec{r}+\Delta\vec{v}\,\Delta t
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta\vec{r}'\coloneqq\vec{r}_{2}'-\vec{r}_{1}',\quad\Delta\vec{r}\coloneqq\vec{r}_{2}-\vec{r}_{1},\quad\Delta\vec{v}\coloneqq\vec{v}_{2}-\vec{v}_{1}
\]

\end_inset

将 
\begin_inset Formula $-\Delta\vec{r}',\Delta\vec{r},\Delta\vec{v}\,\Delta t$
\end_inset

 首尾相连画成三角形，代入余弦定理
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vert\Delta\vec{r}'\vert^{2}=\vert\Delta\vec{r}\vert^{2}+\vert\Delta\vec{v}\,\Delta t\vert^{2}-2\underbrace{\vert\Delta\vec{r}\vert\vert\Delta\vec{v}\,\Delta t\vert\cos\theta}_{-\Delta\vec{r}\cdot\Delta\vec{v}\,\Delta t}
\]

\end_inset

即得关于 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta t$
\end_inset

 的一元二次方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A\,(\Delta t)^{2}+B\,\Delta t+C=0
\]

\end_inset

其中
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
A\coloneqq\Delta\vec{v}\cdot\Delta\vec{v},\quad B\coloneqq2\Delta\vec{r}'\cdot\Delta\vec{v},\quad C\coloneqq\Delta\vec{r}'\cdot\Delta\vec{r}'-\Delta\vec{r}\cdot\Delta\vec{r}
\]

\end_inset

故方程有正实根的条件为
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
B^{2}-4AC>0
\]

\end_inset

此条件满足时，方程有两个正根，应取较小值：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\Delta t=\frac{-\Delta\vec{r}'\cdot\Delta\vec{v}-\sqrt{D}}{\Delta\vec{v}\cdot\Delta\vec{v}},\quad D\coloneqq(\Delta\vec{r}'\cdot\Delta\vec{v})^{2}-(\Delta\vec{v}\cdot\Delta\vec{v})(\Delta\vec{r}'\cdot\Delta\vec{r}'-\Delta\vec{r}\cdot\Delta\vec{r})}
\]

\end_inset


