\begin_layout Subsection
动量在任意惯性系中的变化值
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
另一方面，完全弹性碰撞所造成的动量改变值
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta\vec{p}\coloneqq\vec{p}_{1,0}-\vec{p}_{1,0}'=-(\vec{p}_{2,0}-\vec{p}_{2,0}')
\]

\end_inset

应垂直于碰撞瞬间两圆之切线，亦即平行于碰撞瞬间两圆之连心线。故 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}_{2,0},\Delta\vec{p},-\vec{p}_{2,0}'$
\end_inset

 首尾相连即构成等腰三角形，且 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta\vec{p}$
\end_inset

 的长度为 
\begin_inset Formula $\vec{p}_{2,0}$
\end_inset

 在碰撞瞬间两圆之连心线 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta\vec{r}\coloneqq\vec{r}_{2}-\vec{r}_{1}$
\end_inset

 上投影之二倍：
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\vert\Delta\vec{p}\vert=\vert2\vec{p}_{2,0}\cdot\vec{e}_{\Delta\vec{r}}\vert,\quad\vec{e}_{\Delta\vec{r}}\coloneqq\frac{\Delta\vec{r}}{\vert\Delta\vec{r}\vert}
\]

\end_inset

另据 
\begin_inset Formula $\Delta\vec{p},\Delta\vec{r}$
\end_inset

 之定义，二者应同向，故
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\Delta\vec{p}=\vert\Delta\vec{p}\vert\vec{e}_{\Delta\vec{r}}=\left|2\vec{p}_{2,0}\cdot\frac{\Delta\vec{r}}{\vert\Delta\vec{r}\vert}\right|\frac{\Delta\vec{r}}{\vert\Delta\vec{r}\vert}
\]

\end_inset

综上可得
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\boxed{\Delta\vec{p}=\frac{2m_{1}m_{2}}{m_{1}+m_{2}}\vert\Delta\vec{v}\cdot\Delta\vec{r}\vert\frac{\Delta\vec{r}}{\vert\Delta\vec{r}\vert^{2}},\quad\begin{cases}
\Delta\vec{r}\coloneqq\vec{r}_{2}-\vec{r}_{1}\\
\Delta\vec{v}\coloneqq\vec{v}_{2}-\vec{v}_{1}
\end{cases}}
\]

\end_inset


